    "longBusinessSummary": "Coteccons Construction Joint Stock Company provides designing and construction services in Vietnam. It is involved in the equipment installation, interior decoration, and office leasing related activities; amusement and theme parks activities; and design, construction, and installation services for aluminum, glass, and metal products. The company also offers civil and industrial construction; construction project management consulting; and design and installation services for mechanical and electrical works of construction and other construction systems, as well as software production, computer programming, and commission services; and trades in real estate and construction materials. In addition, it repairs, installs, leases, and sells machinery, equipment, and spare parts. Further, the company engages in renting energy machinery and heating equipment for solar energy. Further, the company is involved in the construction projects, including commercial, residential, infrastructure, hotel and resort, industrial zone, and school and hospital. Coteccons Construction Joint Stock Company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
